commit.message:
Refactor ci pipeline (#1078)

* Split code QC into its own job.

* Remove R install not needed for QC job.

* Add mypy.

* Fix call to mypy to ignore cffi-generated module.

* Install missing mypy types.

* Add requirements file for types.

* Fix build & build sdist split.

* Upload artifacts from builds.

* Fix installation of mypy deps, make build-sdist a requirement for next jobs.

* Install from artifact. Add dep for mypy type checking.

* Hack to install source package in dist/.

* Use hack to name source package in dist/ also when no optional dependency target.

* Try shell: bash to build on Windows.

* fix use of os.linesep to avoid confusion of C compiler on Windows.

* sys/select.h only on POSIX systems.

verification.payload:
tree 4ac66c99e5655cf8a82cd29196d22173543d5f2b
